reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Built for the laptop I purchased and it’s a perfect fit
reviews.reviewText: Built for the laptop I purchased and it’s a perfect fit! There’s more than enough room for cords and peripherals, but it’s still slim enough for under your seat for flights. The anti-theft features make it perfect for travel, or sending it to the library, or wherever else with peace of mind. It’s been pretty durable & rugged so far as well, so top marks for size, durability, and anti-theft features, plus it it still keeps the laptop safe, snug, well cushioned, but it’s not bulky at all and amazingly light weight considering all you get with this laptop bag. The price was quite low for what feels like a custom laptop bag, too, which was a nice bonus as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent backpack for travelling
reviews.reviewText: Excellent for traveling. Although it looks thinner than other backpacks it has good capacity. Took it for trips to Mexico and Japan. Good water protection, but not water proof, as a little of rain water can get through the zippers. The USB cables are a welcomed plus.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this last minute for travel due to the airlines size restrictions. Fast forward 2 years and this has become my go to bag for concerts, events, and travel. It has held up really well and shows no signs of use. I'm pleasantly surprised about it's durability. The locking feature is excellent and I have used the included cable to lock it up. Happy traveler here.
